comments: Green (GSW) reaches in while defending Capela (HOU) and makes clean contact with the ball, leading to the jump ball.
Iguodala (GSW) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) arm during his shooting motion, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) and Durant (GSW) engage off ball before the pass.
LAR shows Harden (HOU) hand checks Durant (GSW) before his upward shooting motion.  RAR shows Harden lands in front of Durant and Durant extends his leg to create contact with Harden.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Durant's (GSW) arm after he has gathered the ball on his driving shot attempt.
RAR shows that Curry (GSW) is moving laterally into Harden's (HOU) path and that the contact causes Harden to go out of bounds.
After the contact, Harden (HOU) steps out of bounds along the sideline.
Harden (HOU) and Durant (GSW) engage off ball before the pass.
RLB shows Harden (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position with a bent forearm to Durant's (GSW) side during his drive.
Paul (HOU) and Green (GSW) engage during the rebound. After Green (GSW) secures the rebound, Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact with Green's hips during the pass.
Thompson (GSW) slides his pivot foot at the end of his dribble.
Iguodala (GSW) and Paul (HOU) engage and disengage after the rebound.
Thompson (GSW) makes contact with Harden (HOU) during his shot attempt that affects his ability to complete his shot.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Tucker's (HOU) path before the contact.
Harden (HOU) steps forward as Green (GSW) retreats, and releases the contact with his off-arm without going through his space.
Harden (HOU) draws Green (GSW) into the air during his shot attempt. Green jumps in front of Harden and would have missed him if Harden hadn't extended his legs.
Thompson (GSW) is in Paul's (HOU) path and turns to beat Paul to the spot before the contact. Paul continues his drive into Thompson.
LAR shows Curry (GSW) makes contact with Gordon's (HOU) arm, affecting his ability to secure the ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: After the contact, Gordon (HOU) steps out of bounds along the sideline.
Paul (HOU) receives a second technical foul for aggressively approaching and making contact with a referee.
